text:
I really enjoyed their crab fried rice, I dont see this being one of their popular dishes however I truly enjoyed it and could not stop thinking about it ever since. Thier matcha is just okay but I didn't have high hopes for that and plus matcha wasn't the main reason why I went.

The service is good, the place is tiny so it managable thouhg I can see how crazy and packed it can get.

This is near chinatown and I highly recommend walking around and up that hill to digest (;
